Package: tmap
Maintainer: Martijn Tennekes <mtennekes@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Title: Thematic Maps
Type: Package
LazyLoad: yes
Author: Martijn Tennekes
Description: Thematic maps are geographical maps in which spatial data
    distributions are visualized. This package offers a flexible, layer-based,
    way to create all kinds of thematic maps, such as choropleths and bubble
    maps.
Version: 0.6
Date: 2014-06-30
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0)
Imports:
    rgeos,
    grid,
    gridBase,
    sp,
    rgdal,
    classInt,
    RColorBrewer,
    igraph,
    fields,
    vegan
Suggests:
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
